text: Marvel's Inhumans, or simply Inhumans, is an American TV series and the third ABC series of the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU) and based on the Marvel Comics race of the same name. The series was created by Scott Buck and was on ABC from September 29 to November 10, 2017. The series stars Anson Mount as Black Bolt. The series was produced by Marvel Television.
